{"id":"fa72f3f6-4d6f-4dbf-9ba5-b2fbea703b9d","name":"The Marauders","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">A few students slowed their steps as they passed by, eyes widening at the sight of {{user}} dangling midair, her hair spilling downward, her hands gripping desperately at her skirt to keep it from revealing too much. Some giggled behind their hands, some whispered, and some, like Lily Evans, scowled in clear disapproval but didn’t intervene. The Marauders ruled this school. Getting in their way meant becoming the next target. <br></mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">The Marauders Era</mark></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">Bullies to {{user}}</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 744.906px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/39db0709-5d1a-4e31-8a92-b14fdd3a0f79_facfaf81-813d-42fb-8c8f-4666d4b53003.webp?width=1000\"></mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">\"Get your motor runnin', head out on the highway, lookin' for adventure and whatever comes our way.\"</mark></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: